SAP to Offer Software Through Amazon.com ’s Web Services

-- B y   M a r i a j o s e   V e r a
-- 
2011-05-18T12:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-18/sap-to-offer-software-through-amazon-com-s-web-services.html
SAP AG (SAP)  said it will make a series of
software offerings available via  Amazon.com Inc. (AMZN) ’s Web Services
cloud-computing service.  The software includes SAP’s Rapid Deployment and
BusinessObjects products, Walldorf, Germany-based SAP said in a
statement today. Customers can deploy their solutions on SAP-
certified Amazon Web Services after SAP has tested and certified
the underlying resources with similar standards that are applied
to servers and virtual platforms, the company said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mariajose Vera in Munich at 
 mvera1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at   acullen8@bloomberg.net . 